data.description: *** OFFER DEADLINE  SET FOR WEDNESDAY  12/13/2023*** NO APPRAISAL OR HOME INSPECTION CONCERN!  Nestled within the tranquil community of Fort Washington, Maryland, and surrounded by the impressive backdrop of the National Harbor, MGM, and the District of Columbia, this captivating 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence perfectly marries comfort and convenience.   Upon entering, this enchanting property greets you with its spacious living areas, a contemporary kitchen, and a serene backyard that exudes peace and tranquility.  The inviting living room is bathed in natural light, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance. The modern kitchen is thoughtfully equipped with updated appliances and ample storage, making it the ideal space for meal preparation and family gatherings.  A cozy family room with a fireplace serves as a haven for gatherings and relaxation. The primary suite boasts a private bathroom and a generous walk-in closet, offering a personal retreat within the home. Three additional, generously proportioned bedrooms provide versatile living spaces. The expansive Sunroom/Florida room enhances the property's charm and adaptability. On the main floor, a private office space is thoughtfully provided for those working from home. As you venture to the basement, you'll discover an expansive area that can be customized to your preferences, whether you envision a private gym or a home theater – this home grants you the space to realize your dreams.  Step outside to the level backyard, where lush landscaping and a stone patio provide the perfect backdrop for serene evenings of entertainment, summer grilling experiences, or ample space for your family and furry friends to roam. The attached garage and driveway ensure parking convenience.  Located in a peaceful neighborhood with amiable neighbors, this home enjoys proximity to parks, schools, shopping, and dining options. Effortless access to major highways simplifies commuting to Washington, D.C.  Whether you're cherishing the tranquility of the backyard or exploring nearby natural parks, 122 Autumn Lake Way offers a contemporary and serene lifestyle. The owner has a Beautiful Cane Corso Dog on site and works from Home. The dog can and will be removed at showing.
